h1. shiro:isLoggedIn

h2. Purpose
Conditionally render the contents of the tag if the current user is fully authenticated.

h2. Examples
{code}
<shiro:isLoggedIn>
    <span>
           Welcome: You have arrived
    </span>
    ...
</shiro:isLoggedIn>


{code}

h2. Description
This tag only writes its body to the output if the user is fully authenticate, defers to SecurityUtils.subject.authenticated. (inversion of [isNotLoggedIn|Tags])



